We have relied on financial statements provided by promoter of the project while issuing Form 3.							
As per the act and regulation, it is mandatory to execute agreement for sale for the units before  receiving amount more than 10 % of the unit consideration amount and report date of AFS to GUJRERA.						
As per Form 3 it is required to report unit wise encumbrnace status at the reporting date. We would like to state that we have obtained  letter from promoter regarding unit wise status of encumbrance for each unit and relied on the same while reporting unit wise status of encumbrance.
